 Readers can scan the QR code in each category to vote or alternatively navigate to the Best Of section on the main page navigation bar on Lowvelder.co.za. Mobile users will have to click on the Menu and then Best of Mbombela will be situated between Network News and Caxton Video.  From here users can select one of the eight main categories in which to vote. Voters will be provided with a form to fill in with your name, surname, email address and phone number. Then you will be allowed to vote for your favourites among the listed businesses on the form. Readers will have to complete at least 80% of the voting form to be considered valid. Voting will be capped via email addresses. Each email can vote once a day in each of the main categories.  Eat, Drink and Be Merry Glam in Mbombela General Services Living in Mbombela Shopping in Mbombela Motoring Kids in Mbombela. 